attributionInfo.agentName: Shell Pointe at Cobblestone Village - Sales Inform

data.description: This charming home is nestled in the well established neighborhood of Marrington Villas at Cobblestone. Upon entry, you are greeted with lovely wood floors and tall, smooth ceilings. This home allows natural light to flood through and create a bright and airy atmosphere. The living room is adorned with a cozy gas log fireplace, perfect for nights in during the chilly winter months. The eat-in kitchen features both recessed & pendant lighting, dazzling countertops, a subway tile backsplash, a large kitchen island, and sleek stainless steel appliances. The spacious master bedroom is complete with a tray ceiling, a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom, with a double vanity, and walk-in tile shower. Step out back and enjoy grilling out or alfresco dining from the back patio.Take advantage of the amenities that Marrington Villas at Cobblestone has to offer, including lawn maintenance, a community pool and a clubhouse. This home is conveniently located a short drive to downtown Summerville and Goose Creek, both of which you will find local shopping, dining and entertainment options. Don't wait! Come see this home today!
